# Infrastructure — Repositories & Runtime (.acm)
> hash: sha256:8b144620deac4697-05d08ecf3f21953e | generated: 2026-03-29 | lines: ~120

## ScriptsLayer
- **Type**: Shell script utilities
- **File**: `scripts/*.sh` (~40 scripts)
- **Purpose**: Automation layer — CI validation, memory storage, confidence calibration, context tracking
- **Dependencies**: bash, git, az cli, gh cli, jq, openssl
- **Public API**:
  - `validate-ci-local.sh` — Run before every push (CHANGELOG + bash + commands)
  - `memory-store.sh` — JSONL append store with dedup and topic_key
  - `confidence-calibrate.sh report` — Monthly NL confidence recalibration
  - `context-tracker.sh log` — Track context usage per command
  - `agent-trace-log.sh` — Append agent invocation traces
  - `confidentiality-sign.sh sign` — SHA-256 sign PR diff before push
  - `push-pr.sh` — CI → sign → commit → push → PR (one command)
  - `session-init.sh` — Session start banner with PAT/profile/branch status
  - `readiness-check.sh` — Verify PAT, profile, tools before operating

## ProfilesStorage
- **Type**: User/company identity storage (N3 local)
- **File**: `.claude/profiles/`
- **Purpose**: Personalize Savia per user — loaded progressively via context-map
- **Dependencies**: active-user.md (pointer), Claude Code auto-memory (~/.claude/projects/*/memory/)
- **Structure**:
  - `users/{slug}/` — identity.md, tone.md, workflow.md, tools.md, preferences.md, accessibility.md, competence.md
  - `company/` — identity.md, technology.md, culture.md
  - `active-user.md` — currently active user slug (gitignored)
  - `savia.md` — Savia's own personality definition
- **Privacy**: N3 — gitignored; personal vault at `~/.savia/personal-vault/`
- **Load strategy**: Lazy — only fragments needed for current command

## ProjectsStorage
- **Type**: Client project data (N4 gitignored)
- **File**: `projects/{proyecto}/`
- **Purpose**: Isolated client/project context — never mixed across projects
- **Dependencies**: CLAUDE.local.md (index), project CLAUDE.md (per-project entry point)
- **Structure per project**:
  - `CLAUDE.md` — project config, environments, team
  - `backlog/`, `specs/`, `reglas-negocio.md`, `equipo.md`
  - `agent-memory/{agent}/` — project-level agent memory (N4)
  - `security/` — security audit reports
  - `_digest-log.md` — idempotency log for all digested documents
- **Privacy**: N4 — ALL client data isolated here; zero leakage to N1 public repo
- **Agent memory isolation**: public(`public-agent-memory/`) → private(`private-agent-memory/`) → project(`projects/{p}/agent-memory/`)

## OutputStorage
- **Type**: Generated artifacts (gitignored)
- **File**: `output/`
- **Purpose**: Store all command outputs — reports, audits, agent runs, test results
- **Dependencies**: commands (write here), reporting skills
- **Naming convention**: `YYYYMMDD-tipo-proyecto.ext`
- **Key subdirs**:
  - `output/audits/` — project audit reports
  - `output/agent-runs/` — autonomous agent logs (overnight-sprint, code-improvement)
  - `output/ast-quality/` — quality gate reports per file
  - `output/dev-sessions/` — dev-session state files and slice outputs
  - `output/coverage-report/` — test coverage summaries
  - `output/postmortems/` — incident postmortem reports
- **Privacy**: N4 — gitignored; may contain client data

## HooksRuntime
- **Type**: Lifecycle hook runtime
- **File**: `.claude/hooks/`, `.claude/settings.json`
- **Purpose**: Deterministic enforcement layer — fires on Claude Code events regardless of LLM instructions
- **Dependencies**: lib/profile-gate.sh, SAVIA_HOOK_PROFILE env var
- **Event coverage**: SessionStart(1), PreToolUse(5 blocking), PostToolUse(async), Stop(1), SubagentStop(1)
- **Profile-gated tiers**:
  - `security` (always): credential-leak, force-push, infra-destructive, data-sovereignty
  - `standard` (default): bash-validate, plan-gate, whitelist, tdd-gate, scope-guard, compliance, premerge, commit-prompt
  - `strict` (pre-release): +agent-dispatch-validate, stop-quality-gate, competence-tracker
  - `ci` (pipelines): non-interactive standard
- **Change profile**: `bash scripts/hook-profile.sh set {profile}` or `SAVIA_HOOK_PROFILE=ci`
